_sText: I've made 25 plus maps and I figured I might as well make a fun gun game map with my favorite 8-10 maps in it. You start in an arena and the first person to rush forward through the gate gets to choose which of my maps the whole server gets to play. Instructions: - Make sure your server has !noblock turned on for this map or everyone will get stuck Maps in gg_wander_party: -gg_school_days (check it out here) -gg_excavation (check it out here) -gg_slide (new map) -gg_balderdash (check it out here) -gg_four_towers (check it out here) -gg_mini_house_blue (check it out here) -gg_dos_pisos (check it out here) -gg_moose_arena (check it out here) -gg_rad_cock (check it out here)
